2) Write a Python program to Remove duplicate characters from a string also 
replace every space with an underscore _ and Display the modified string.

s = input("Enter a string: ")
s = s.replace(" ", "_")
result = ""
for ch in s:
 if ch not in result:
 result += ch
print("Modified string:", result)

